Name: "Crack & Bolt" Fish Jar
AttributesDescription: Grants 50% Basic Attack DMG Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription:
A Royan specialty strictly banned from the Startorch Academy. Salted fish is packed into a jar and sealed with wet clay, allowing it to ferment and develop a strong, distinctive flavor. To eat it, one must crack open the top of the jar.

Before eating it, make sure to keep these things in your mind:
1. Always open the jar outdoors, in a wide and downwind spot.
2. Never open it indoors, in a warm place, upwind, or near a crowd.
3. Check the jar before eating. If you see a crack, put it down immediately and bolt.
